# Sky culture name
msgid "Sardinian"
msgstr "Sardo"

# Sky culture introduction section in markdown format
msgid ""
"Like all peoples of the world, even the ancient Sardinians, turned their "
"eyes to the sky that marked the time and the seasons. The peasant's world "
"has given its name to the stars and the constellations of the Sardinian "
"culture."
msgstr ""
"Como todos los pueblos del mundo, incluso los antiguos sardos, volvieron la "
"vista hacia el cielo que marcaba el tiempo y las estaciones. El mundo "
"campesino ha dado su nombre a las estrellas y las constelaciones de la "
"cultura sarda."

